          <td id="textshadow"><b>Secretlab</b> was founded by two former competitive gamers Ian Alexander Ang and Alaric Choo in 2014.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td id="textshadow">The company officially launched in Singapore, Malaysia and Australia in May 2015 and followed by the United States in 2016.</td>
