    <div class="story-image" id="story">
      <div class="story">
        <div class="title">
          <h1>Story</h1>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-container">
      <div class="column">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="box">
            <p>
              Secretlab was founded in 2014 by Ian Alexander Ang and Alaric Choo . They got the idea to start the company after they could not find a chair that could be used for long hours and fit both gaming and office setups.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="box">
            <p>  
              Secretlab founders use a direct-to-consumer distribution model to keep prices down. In September 2020, The company was ranked third on Singapore’s top 10 startups by LinkedIn, and CEO Ian Alexander Ang was named EY Entrepreneur Of The Year for Consumer Products, the youngest in the history of the award 
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="box">
          <p>
            They got the idea to start the company after they could not find a chair that could be used for long hours and fit both gaming and office setups. The company officially launched in Singapore in May 2015 and later in the same year launched in Malaysia and Australia followed by the United States in 2016.
          </p>
          </div>
          <div class="box">
          <div>
            <p>In 2017, the company expanded into the United Kingdom, Europe and Canada.</p>
            <p>In 2019, Secretlab expanded within the South-east Asia region and into the Philippines, Thailand and Indonesia.</p>
            <p>In 2020, The company moved into Korea, Japan, and New Zealand, part of its expansion into the Asia-Pacific region.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="products" id="products">
      <div class="products-image">  
      <div class="title">
        <h1>Products</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="paragraph">
      <p>Secretlab's products are generally targeted at gamers, although the company has also attracted customers from law firms, clinics and corporate offices.</p>
      <br>
      <p>The company has released four models, the <strong>Secretlab THRONE</strong> ,<strong>Secretlab TITAN XL</strong>, <strong>Secretlab Titan</strong> , and <strong>Secretlab OMEGA</strong> .The models were revised and sold as the SecretLab 2020 Series in May 2019 after three years of research and development.</p>
      <br>
      <p>The chair's cushion are made with high density cold-cure foam with metal substructure and sold with various upholstery options, including leather, fabric, and leatherette.</p>
    </div>
